WEBVTT

00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:05.451

00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:12.200
♪In the old house, a light breeze blows♪

00:00:12.200 --> 00:00:14.560
♪Carrying a wisp of floral fragrance♪

00:00:17.120 --> 00:00:19.400
♪You left in such haste,
without hesitation♪

00:00:19.400 --> 00:00:22.040
♪Before I could even feel the joy♪

00:00:23.760 --> 00:00:25.960
♪I dared not write a single word♪

00:00:25.960 --> 00:00:28.680
♪Afraid it would give my heart away♪

00:00:29.080 --> 00:00:33.640
♪Leaving behind a foolish soul
in loneliness♪

00:00:35.640 --> 00:00:37.040
♪The world grows old♪

00:00:37.040 --> 00:00:38.640
♪Time slips by like a blade♪

00:00:38.640 --> 00:00:41.720
♪Through every day and night
as I wait for the flowers to bloom♪

00:00:42.080 --> 00:00:44.160
♪It feels as though
a thousand years never passed♪

00:00:44.160 --> 00:00:48.320
♪The wind lets petals
fall into your palm♪

00:00:48.320 --> 00:00:51.640
♪Love makes us foolish,
lost in endless memories♪

00:00:51.640 --> 00:00:54.840
♪No one cares about our story♪

00:00:54.880 --> 00:00:56.680
♪Slowly fading away♪

00:00:56.680 --> 00:01:00.840
♪Flowers bloom in snow,
brief as life itself♪

00:01:01.040 --> 00:01:04.680
♪So many poems through the ages
speak of♪

00:01:04.680 --> 00:01:08.480
♪Love and hatred,
partings and vows of the past♪

00:01:08.480 --> 00:01:10.800
♪Had we never crossed paths
in this lifetime♪

00:01:10.800 --> 00:01:13.800
♪Nothing could separate us,
even if we were oceans apart♪

00:01:19.680 --> 00:01:22.880
=The Princess Decree=

00:01:22.880 --> 00:01:24.820
=Episode 15=

00:01:36.480 --> 00:01:37.519
Go check over there.

00:01:38.200 --> 00:01:38.879
Search carefully.

00:01:39.159 --> 00:01:39.519
Yes.

00:02:04.920 --> 00:02:05.640
Someone's there.

00:02:05.640 --> 00:02:06.480
Go take a look.

00:02:45.820 --> 00:02:47.860
♪Autumn goes and winter comes♪

00:02:47.860 --> 00:02:51.900
♪Cold currents on the river,
leaning long by the railing♪

00:02:52.300 --> 00:02:54.020
♪Red plum blooming alone♪

00:02:54.020 --> 00:02:58.460
♪Coolness in my sleeves,
I drink the leftover wine alone♪

00:02:58.460 --> 00:03:02.900
♪The moon rises above,
while the jade tower remains♪

00:03:02.900 --> 00:03:05.340
♪Go or stay as you wish♪

00:03:05.340 --> 00:03:08.380
♪Longing in my throat,
never ceasing love and hate♪

00:03:08.380 --> 00:03:11.340
♪Break off a willow branch♪

00:03:11.340 --> 00:03:14.140
♪Time doesn't fail the years♪

00:03:14.140 --> 00:03:17.820
♪Tenderness continues like spring water♪

00:03:17.820 --> 00:03:20.260
♪I drink a thousand cups
without drunkenness♪

00:03:20.260 --> 00:03:24.180
♪Yet I grow weary and pale for my love♪

00:03:24.180 --> 00:03:28.580
♪Fearless in a big dream,
my heart about to break♪

00:03:28.580 --> 00:03:31.220
♪How many times has love been wounded?♪

00:03:31.340 --> 00:03:33.660
♪Ask those who have gone far away♪

00:03:33.660 --> 00:03:36.780
♪When can they return westward?♪

00:04:03.860 --> 00:04:05.700
♪Autumn goes and winter comes♪

00:04:09.039 --> 00:04:10.159
They're gone.

00:04:11.680 --> 00:04:13.000
Let's hurry back to the city.

